title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“ 'No one expected it to be that high, but it's lower than what we expected,' said Mark Obrinsky,...”. [From The Wall Street Journal, 5 July 1991, page A8. Submitted by Bernard M. Brenner, Chelmsford, Massachusetts.]
